text: The Harbourfront Landmark is a skyscraper in Hong Kong, China. It is 233 meters (763 feet) tall and has 70 floors. It was built in 2001 and is one of the tallest buildings in the world. ==Related pages== * List of tallest buildings in the world ==Other websites== *Emporis.com – The Harbourfront Landmark *SkycraperPage.com – The Harbourfront Landmark Category:Skyscrapers in China Category:Buildings and structures in Hong Kong
